    FROM pkbperson AS person
    INNER JOIN personcontact AS pc ON person.id = pc.person_id
    INNER JOIN core.account AS account ON person.defaultaccountid = account.id
    WHERE
        pc.contactvalue = 'bz.patient.1@pkbtest.com'
